Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟雾弹 手榴弹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个乱来的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能循着气味追踪么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宪兵大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把她带到安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉 阿尔还在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 回来后我全跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我就只能等待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于8区圣路易大道保护少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是钢之炼金术师阁下的亲属
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护送她到中央司令部 重复
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)\fad(0,500)}于8区圣路易大道保护少女 似乎是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去掩护他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:02:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郊外有间可用的空屋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里会合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心别被跟踪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有进展的话就联络您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您绝不可以去现场哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太缠人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐走到没人的地方了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被设计了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？伤疤男么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去解决那边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边由我来动手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左臂已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:03:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经派不上用处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我这样的下人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连少主都倒下的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无民则无从为王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但王若不在 民则无去无从
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是为了我们一族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主您也必须要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会抛弃你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了大义 又有什么不能抛弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰芳 你要做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这铠甲里面是空的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成如此不幸的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要相信炼金术么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身体有诸多不便之处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 不便不等于不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有必要被你同情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哥哥用炼金术给我留下的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等于否定哥哥 否定炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信炼金术的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要相信！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 温莉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.93,0:05:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丢脸 又弄哭她了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥总是粗心大意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还让她看到那么血腥的场面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 从头来过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修瓦尔人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那刺青
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快闪开！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结实的铁索！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再生力过强适得其反了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从内侧涨起的肉会把你自己绑住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到了 人造人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆了你们一道了 该死的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？人造人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放上来 准备逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 霍…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宪兵来了 装不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了 快抓住伤疤男！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐虽然讨厌 但可以信任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的问题是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住伤疤男 阿尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害洛克贝尔夫妇之罪 以及其他种种
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备接受审判吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 仆从先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢对我恩人尤基先生的仆从动手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这豆丁男
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么！你这豆丁女！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小孩是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐离远点 这里很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好汉架不住人多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那炼金术是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远程炼成？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤疤男！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说过你的事情 姚麟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在直接去秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有个同伴 带上她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 没这个时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 她快死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等我去接她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你动作快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人应该是玛斯坦那里的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胆子不小啊 小鬼
Comment: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是那种眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论走到哪里 憎恨就只会带来憎恨么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样血应该止住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宪兵队到这附近来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙负伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该没有逃远
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我一点不漏的搜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老兄 快点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.38,0:11:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅 快逃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.18,0:11:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你呀 这种紧要关头还乱捡东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:12:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 它身处危急之中一个人好孤单呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捡了野猫回来就偷偷养在自己肚子里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你真没人性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看它这么乖的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的啦 你放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布拉德雷总统
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说你们的青梅竹马被保护了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精英人才的亲友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么能怠慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 小妹妹 我先告退了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 您太客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个率直的好姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要珍惜她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好的 你要把爸爸妈妈的事都讲给我听
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们直到最后都全力救治别人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:14:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我还是希望他们能活着回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我除了等待什么都干不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 正好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克贝尔小姐 有您的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加菲尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊 温莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来以为我一个人怎么也能应付...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉妹妹还没回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看吧 不是温莉妹妹根本修不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的顾客们实在是太难伺候啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点回来吧 温莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:14:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐快点回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其让加菲尔叔叔弄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腿还是姐姐你弄一下比较好用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉啊 上次你帮我取型的假腿装饰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你尽快啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的胳膊也拜托你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我这边先的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想尽快见到你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 温莉妹妹是我们大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啦 我这就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家等我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力的 会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 谢谢你阻止了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多人都在等着我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一点我就没有颜面去见他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:15:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德 不可以忘记保养你的机械铠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次给你寄好用的上光油哦 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你说啥？没听到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见啦 温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 爱德 你说了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次若再令你哭泣 那一定是喜悦的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个一定会恢复原来的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你喜极而泣！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我记住吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我手和脚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经没有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就喜欢上他了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上车
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个重伤员需要医生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又拉我上贼船？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个坏小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得您有家室
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果觉得麻烦就请拒绝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿家伙 你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从伊修瓦尔回来就跟老婆分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切掉胳膊后走进下水道？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想得破伤风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我只摆弄尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下手有点粗暴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.78,0:18:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别自作多情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出这个计划的是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为利害一致才协助你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了长生不老 我出国时已经有牺牲的觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还是不够
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我来 兰芳觉悟更高
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那招陷阱还不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没法再用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要替代的胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我会给你介绍个好机械铠技师的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.68,0:19:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是国军上校 罗伊·玛斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新国第十二皇子姚麟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你帮忙找来医生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该道谢的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚·罗斯一事给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这次的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做格拉特尼的人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这家伙跟部分军部高层有关联
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一部分？岂止！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金·布拉德雷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能也是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼罩下面的眼球上有噬身蛇的刺青
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和格拉特尼一起把我们逼到绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家最高领导是人造人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布拉德雷身上并没有格拉特尼般的非人气息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和普通人类的气息没有区别
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:20:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先如果总统是人造人 那他的孩子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造人是没有生殖能力的 书上有写过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.98,0:21:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他儿子塞利姆是收养的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是亲生儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.78,0:21:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他是人是妖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之把他拉下总统的位子变得容易多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先从这家伙身上挖些情报
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有贤者之石也拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.48,0:21:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定可以用来治疗我的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这可是兰芳牺牲一条手臂才抓住的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是长生不老的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把他带回新国
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.38,0:21:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这边找了这么久恢复身体的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.58,0:21:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能让你拿着就跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.98,0:21:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 麟你是偷渡进来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 没空陪你们闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.88,0:21:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛斯坦老弟 我先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:22:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了拉丝特的 玛斯坦上校！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊·玛斯坦！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.98,0:22:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Comment: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.38,0:24:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善意与亲切的微笑背后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.18,0:24:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知隐藏何物的密林之中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.58,0:24:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探寻的手段需要慎重
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.08,0:24:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗中摸索前行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.68,0:24:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.58,0:24:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.28,0:24:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第24话 腹中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.28,0:24:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待鲁莽的闯入者的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.68,0:24:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那无边的黑暗
